race.comment: SIX OF WANDS (2) has come back in fine fashion stringing back-to-back wins together with Sandkuhl being in the saddle for that last-start victory over this course and distance. Again gets the benefit of her 2kg claim and should be right there when the judge calls a halt. LAND BANK (7) has placed two from three over this distance range and looks to be working up to another win. Has to be included in calculations. ROCKRATA (21) was a touch disappointing at the latest effort but the form prior was full of merit. Worth another chance from the inside alley. I STOLE IT (5) best of the rest with the 3kg claim.
